                  Â© 2014 AT&amp;T Intellectual Property. All rights reserved. 
                  <a href="https://developer.att.com/" target="_blank">https://developer.att.com</a>
                  </p>
                </div> <!-- end of ft -->
              </div> <!-- end of footer -->
            </div> <!-- end of page_container -->
          </body>
        </html>
